2. cs.MM (Multimedia) - Image enhancement is a common topic in multimedia research and this paper specifically focuses on evaluating different techniques for enhancing image contrast and preserving brightness. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - Image enhancement is also relevant in information retrieval, particularly in improving the quality of images for visual search and analysis. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) - Image enhancement is a common topic in graphics research, particularly in improving the visual quality of images for display and printing. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - Since the paper evaluates different image enhancement techniques based on various metrics, it can also be relevant to multimedia research that focuses on evaluating the quality of multimedia content.
